Available Tools: get_current_weather | get_feels_like | get_pressure | get_visibility
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "location": "string", "metrics": ["string"] }
Response Schema: { "location": "string", "metrics": { "temperature": number, "humidity": number, "pressure": number } }
---
Question: What is the feels-like temperature and barometric pressure in Paris right now?
Call: { "func_call": "get_feels_like", "location": "Paris, France", "metrics": ["feels_like", "pressure"] }
Response: { "location": "Paris, France", "metrics": { "temperature": 14.2, "humidity": 68, "pressure": 1011.5 } }

Question: I need the apparent temperature and air pressure for Berlin.
Call: { "func_call": "get_feels_like", "location": "Berlin, Germany", "metrics": ["feels_like", "pressure"] }
Response: { "location": "Berlin, Germany", "metrics": { "temperature": 9.8, "humidity": 52, "pressure": 1016.3 } }

